Name: CIRCULARIZE ORBIT
checklistText:
<size=24>CIRCULARIZE ORBIT</size>

<size=22>Computer:</size>
- Set Ap (core 57) and Pe (core 56) to your destination target.
- Read time to Ap (core 73) and Pe (core 74)

<size=22>The Hohmann Transfer:</size>
At Apogee:
- Burn so IVI's read zero

Ap Perigee:
- Burn so IVI's read zero
